µJCµC6Shit, I forgot to read JP! ;-)


µJEµC0The first day then was full of little conversations and lots of different beers (Swedish, Danish, German and Spanish), ending up half drunken for me. I went to the basement for some hours of sleep. Luckily I had those earplugs, without you'll loose agains that snoring sceners. And there were lots of them hiding in the darkness like zombies trying to steal your sleep. I won the fight and got nice 6 hours of fine sleep, fresh enough to start the day. As usual I wanted to take a shower but hey...there were no showers.

µC0Damn, I felt dirty, what to do now? Esau, Pezac and some more guys decided to drive to the beach to check out the temperatur of the sea. Was it really as cold as everyone thinks? We went to find out the truth. 10 Minutes later we reached a place to enter the water, but the ground was slimy, trying to swallow and eat you, ready to catch your life. We retired from the slimy monster ground and walked a bit further to a little harbor. It was more easy to get into the water there. So this is what we did: we used that cold water to shrink our dicks to the size of a match. It worked pritty well and fast with only some degrees above zero, at least this is how it felt. :) Damn myself, I had those white pants and if you've ever watched a wet t-shirt show you know what happens if white clothes gets wet. :) Anyway we felt really good after this stone age washing and were ready for another nice party day. So we started with some beer and barbecue of course.

µC0Later Kufa and some other sceners had the same bath as we had before. And because I wanted to see their dicks shrink, too, I followed them to the water and we had much fun, this time I had not to freeze in the water but the others. :)

µC0Back at the party place the time flew by and it should have been compo time. I really don't know how they managed that big delay, but the compos planned for Saturday were all held on Sunday, right before the voting, which was right before the price giving. Anyway we really had no problems to fill up the day and the night with even more beer, barbecue and lots of small talks to sceners. As the sun was shining the real party was outside, you know. So we not only grilled some meat on the grill but also grilled our skin in the sun. Soon a lot of red skins were running around and it felt a bit like the wild western times with all those red skinned indians running around (including me of course). :)

µC0Late at night Kufa brought some Whisky to drink and there was also some strange Wodka mix from Malmis. I tried both and it tasted very well. The only disadvantage was that the alcohol started to control everything of my body. So while waiting for the demo/intro competition which should have been started somewhen in the night I felt asleep under a table in front of the bigscreen. Luckily I woke up just some minutes later, but I decided that I really need some hours of sleep now even if I would miss the Demo/Intro compo. I went down to the basement, you know, the place with the snoring zombies, and took another 8 hours of sleep. That was good.

µC0But while having that nice dreams of undressed girls dancing one the stage (you know, that dreams you have if you are running around with "dicke eier") somebody switched on the light, clapped the hands and said something in Swedish which I didn't understood. Someone translated it for me later and it should have meant that the last compos (gfx and music) will start now and we should get up quickly. Actually it was not hard to understand the "get up quickly" as she expressed herself quite well with her actions. :)
